(138, '_transient_dash_01e18dead815ce736e3b9cccfbd773a5', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'https://wordpress.org/news/2017/06/evans/\'>WordPress 4.8 “Evans”</a> <span class="rss-date">8 de junho de 2017</span><div class="rssSummary">An Update with You in Mind Gear up for a more intuitive WordPress! Version 4.8 of WordPress, named “Evans” in honor of jazz pianist and composer William John “Bill” Evans, is available for download or update in your WordPress dashboard. New features in 4.8 add more ways for you to express yourself and represent your brand. Though some [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'https://wptavern.com/popular-wordpress-plugins-slow-to-add-meta-box-support-for-calypso\'>WPTavern: Popular WordPress Plugins Slow to Add Meta Box Support for Calypso</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'https://wptavern.com/wordcamp-netherlands-reinstated-for-2018\'>WPTavern: WordCamp Netherlands Reinstated for 2018</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'https://wptavern.com/wpweekly-episode-279-the-future-of-underscores-with-david-a-kennedy\'>WPTavern: WPWeekly Episode 279 – The Future of Underscores with David A. Kennedy</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class="dashboard-news-plugin"><span>Plugins populares:</span> Limit Login Attempts&nbsp;<a href="plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=limit-login-attempts&amp;_wpnonce=424850152a&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800" class="thickbox open-plugin-details-modal" aria-label="Instalar Limit Login Attempts">(Instalar)</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
